</span><span begin="33.073" end="33.207">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">贯彻正义一途</span></p><p begin="34.132" end="37.655" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="34.132" end="34.680">時</span><span begin="34.680" end="34.991">を</span><span begin="36.228" end="36.508">か</span><span begin="36.508" end="36.854">す</span><span begin="36.854" end="37.070">め</span><span begin="37.070" end="37.655">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">掠过时光长流</span></p><p begin="38.003" end="43.884" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="38.003" end="39.232">剥</span><span begin="39.361" end="39.659">が</span><span begin="39.659" end="40.587">れ</span><span begin="40.944" end="41.154">落</span><span begin="41.154" end="42.270">ち</span><span begin="42.270" end="42.552">て</span><span begin="42.552" end="42.813">い</span><span begin="42.813" end="43.884">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">片片剥落而去</span></p><p begin="44.329" end="50.106" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.329" end="45.533">羽</span><span begin="45.680" end="45.944">根</span><span begin="45.944" end="46.898">と</span><span begin="47.229" end="47.581">暮</span><span begin="47.581" end="48.641">れ</span><span begin="48.641" end="48.837">の</span><span begin="48.837" end="50.106">声</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">羽毛与终暮之声</span></p><p begin="50.620" end="56.422" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="50.620" end="51.772">褪</span><span begin="51.772" end="52.211">せ</span><span begin="52.211" end="53.064">た</span><span begin="53.273" end="53.897">空</span><span begin="53.897" end="54.424">を</span><span begin="54.424" end="54.975">満</span><span begin="54.975" end="55.137">た</span><span begin="55.137" end="55.407">し</span><span begin="55.407" end="55.795">て</span><span begin="55.795" end="56.014">ゆ</span><span begin="56.014" end="56.422">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">渐渐填满黯空</span></p><p begin="56.726" end="1:01.895" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.726" end="57.473">飾</span><span begin="57.561" end="57.828">ら</span><span begin="57.828" end="58.361">な</span><span begin="58.361" end="58.603">い</span><span begin="58.603" end="59.129">モ</span><span begin="59.402" end="1:00.185">ノ</span><span begin="1:00.185" end="1:01.895">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">以不加修饰之物</span></p><p begin="1:03.356" end="1:09.042" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:03.356" end="1:04.517">何</span><span begin="1:04.517" end="1:04.904">故</span><span begin="1:04.904" end="1:05.922">か</span><span begin="1:06.220" end="1:06.454">こ</span><span begin="1:06.454" end="1:07.606">ぼ</span><span begin="1:07.606" end="1:07.830">れ</span><span begin="1:07.830" end="1:08.014">て</span><span begin="1:08.014" end="1:08.097">い</span><span begin="1:08.097" end="1:09.042">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">像汗滴一样的水珠</span></p><p begin="1:09.487" end="1:15.456" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:09.487" end="1:11.238">汗</span><span begin="1:11.238" end="1:12.151">の</span><span begin="1:12.489" end="1:12.817">よ</span><span begin="1:12.817" end="1:13.886">う</span><span begin="1:13.886" end="1:14.003">な</span><span begin="1:14.003" end="1:14.418">ソ</span><span begin="1:14.418" end="1:15.456">レ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">不知为何沿脸颊滑落</span></p><p begin="1:15.770" end="1:21.719" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:15.770" end="1:17.565">雨</span><span begin="1:17.565" end="1:18.455">と</span><span begin="1:18.845" end="1:19.159">誤</span><span begin="1:19.159" end="1:19.654">魔</span><span begin="1:19.654" end="1:20.047">化</span><span begin="1:20.047" end="1:20.464">す</span><span begin="1:20.464" end="1:20.686">以</span><span begin="1:20.686" end="1:21.230">外</span><span begin="1:21.230" end="1:21.719">は</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我只得掩饰 称之为雨</span></p><p begin="1:21.930" end="1:27.06